{"tid":1369866,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我覺得不論呢場運動點收場都好，之後警隊都會被政府收皮","createTime":"2019-07-26T20:50:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T03:53:03.000Z","uid":206617,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"364dd95c15de0d90b7bc62cf393559d96b9fa452","tid":1369866,"uid":206617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T20:50:14.000Z","msg":"早幾日已經同個朋友討論警權過大既問題<br />\n<br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n朋友：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：其實我覺得政府遲早會處理警權問題<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：下？點會？林鄭講明會撐佢地嫁喎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：你唔覺得家下班狗完全無視哂法律嫁咩？只要上面攬佢，基本上佢地呢D執法者，完全可以唔理法律嫁喎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：但都唔會削佢地警權<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：或者林鄭唔會驚，但係下個上位既，會唔驚？你估張建宗上位之後，會唔會驚呀拿？班狗係全港最多槍嫁喎，但佢地可以無視法律嫁喎？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：你都ON9，班警察撐政府嫁嘛<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：但唔係呢&hellip;&hellip;當權者唔係直接對班警察嫁嘛，佢真係會唔驚咩？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然後點知今日就黎一單，張建宗VS警察<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後張建宗仲要秒跪<br />\n<br />\n睇番個ORG CHART，張建宗係警察既老頂個老頂個老頂，只係衰在冇炮，但結果俾班警察屌到極速投降<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇怕張建宗都唔洗做特首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />連下屬既威脅都驚<br />\n不過，假如連香港既二哥都驚班狗，你地估下林鄭，又或者下任驚唔驚呀拿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n家下政府要對付示威者，先要用班狗<br />\n但你地估下，當呢場運動完左之後，一班夠膽咁串去威脅上司，甚至公開講話『唔道歉就不支持』，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>特首會容許呢種威脅存在？</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n講好聽D<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">狡兔死，走狗烹</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n冇錯呀，講緊你呀，MON緊POST既<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">CONDAM</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n囂張過頭，連二哥都敢串，準備件事完左之被人削啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n分分鐘就因為佐級封信，直頭<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>轉頭政府覺得要趁機透過獨立委員會去削鳩你地</strong></span>TIM呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解？<br />\n1. 你地枝炮威脅到佢地<br />\n2. 你地只認直屬上司，唔認政府機關，唔認二哥<br />\n3. 削鳩你地又可以平民憤，點解唔做？<br />\n讀得書少，就睇番多D中史書啦"},{"pid":"60d178a978dfee315c3605f7573f8e80d9e8aa7d","tid":1369866,"uid":206617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T20:54:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fff2c3d86997dcdc05d6c15ca747edede872d884","tid":1369866,"uid":267600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T21:03:25.000Z","msg":"有道理！推！"},{"pid":"1d066d7e6b94ce45bb77abdce82a3e8df398f4da","tid":1369866,"uid":65738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T21:04:51.000Z","msg":"佢攪小張單野，一定觸動中共神經，中共要狗，不是要狼"},{"pid":"4bfaa74dfccd2a1fdc1bb7880b85e374cbb97f84","tid":1369866,"uid":206617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fff2c3d86997dcdc05d6c15ca747edede872d884","tid":1369866,"uid":267600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T21:03:25.000Z","msg":"有道理！推！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T21:04:59.000Z","msg":"多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07b2a57e2a7f30ee2c1350bd6500c32d61ec1e5f","tid":1369866,"uid":206617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d066d7e6b94ce45bb77abdce82a3e8df398f4da","tid":1369866,"uid":65738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T21:04:51.000Z","msg":"佢攪小張單野，一定觸動中共神經，中共要狗，不是要狼"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T21:06:11.000Z","msg":"其實係<br />\n唔好話中共，港共都有隱憂啦<br />\n家下壇野明顯係恃住政府冇左佢地唔得咁"},{"pid":"63535a52455ed9313aa7f8c57a10540f8eeb6c33","tid":1369866,"uid":65738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T21:09:41.000Z","msg":"歷史loop:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">年羹堯</span>，字亮工、雙峯，號雙峰，清朝康熙和雍正年間重要將領。原籍安徽懷遠，改隸漢軍鑲黃旗，同進士出身。雍正帝的敦肅皇貴妃之兄。 年羹堯和隆科多在擁立雍正帝即位時發揮重要作用，人稱「內有隆科多，外有年羹堯」。曾平定青海叛亂，深得雍正賞識，官至撫遠大將軍、一等公，權傾一時。後來失勢，被雍正帝賜死。&nbsp;"},{"pid":"2afc770f2016ae2741ddba364c964ca5738a5e01","tid":1369866,"uid":81071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T21:11:34.000Z","msg":"其實唔洗擔心.....<br />\n佢地死硬<br />\n<br />\n我地win 就直接開佢波<br />\n<br />\n我地 lose<br />\n他日香港清洗完太平地之後<br />\n<br />\n你覺得中共會容許一個 全球最後一支粵系武裝部隊繼續存在？"},{"pid":"88fc0969410a39531a0c98950a53dea9b77325fb","tid":1369866,"uid":272474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T21:12:07.000Z","msg":"好難講 <br />\n警隊個邊背後有極左勢力加持<br />\n如果唔係點解可以咁惡，呢個現象由626 個急症室私隱 Behave youself封信開始正式確立"},{"pid":"dbf5f5df3bbecfad6990a0a646c12d9513b14531","tid":1369866,"uid":206617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T03:53:03.000Z","msg":"推番上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}